name: WATER you doing? We hate floodgates
description: Negate the first effect of "Ocean Dragon Lord - Kairyu-Shin". This Skill cannot leave your inventory.

name: Eternal Hellfire
description: "Molten Zombie" is treated always treated as a Zombie monster

name: Pile of Old Bones
description: If you would Fusion Summon a Zombie monster using a "Skull Servant" you control, you can banish monsters from your GY as material as well

name: Partial Zombification
description: While "Zombie World" is face-up on the field, monsters your opponent controls and in their GY do not become Zombie monsters, but are also treated as Zombie monsters instead. Negate the second effect of "Zombie World". This Skill cannot leave your inventory.

name: Scythe and Dice
description: If you would activate the effect of "Edge Imp Scythe", you can discard it and use Patchwork instead.

name: Uncracking Kraken
description: "Frightfur Kraken" cannot attack the turn you use the first effect of "Frightfur Kraken". This Skill cannot leave your inventory.

name: Missing Piece
description: You cannot Fusion Summon "Frightfur Sabre-Tooth" using more than 2 Fusion Materials. This Skill cannot leave your inventory.

name: Construct Constriction
description: You can only use each effect of "El Shaddoll Construct" once per turn. This Skill cannot leave your inventory

name: Cold Fire
description: Your opponent takes no damage from the effects of "Volcanic Emperor". Negate the first effect of "Volcanic Inferno". This Skill cannot leave your inventory

name: Everlasting Burning
description: "Ashened" monsters and "Veidos the Eruption Dragon of Extinction" are always treated as FIRE monsters, The second effect of "Veidos the Eruption Dragon of Extinction" instead destroys 1 monster on the field. This Skill cannot leave your inventory.

name: We Are Venom
description: While you control "Venom Swamp", all Reptile monsters you control are treated as "Venom" monsters.

name: A Good Offense
description: Negate the first effect of "Cosmic Slicer Zer'oll". This Skill cannot leave your inventory.

name: Entrop takes an L
description: The second effect of "Magician of Chaos" can only be activated during your turn. This Skill cannot leave your inventory.

name: Mythical Mishaps
description: You cannot activate the monster effect of "Mythical Beast Jackal King" and "Mythical Beast Master Cerberus". This Skill cannot leave your inventory.

name: Don't Be Greedy
description: Negate the second effect of "Greedy Venom Fusion Dragon". You can only use each effect of "Predaplant Chimerafflesia" once per turn. This Skill cannot leave your inventory.

name: Mag-NO-lia
description: The third effect of "Aromalylith Magnolia" only gives itself ATK points. This Skill cannot leave your inventory.

name: Ed… ward…?
description: You can Fusion Summon "Chimera the Flying Mythical Beast" by banishing 1 of the materials from your GY and Tributing the other from your hand or field. "Berfomet" is now treated as a Flip Monster.

name: Fake Tarot Cards
description: The effects of "Prediction Princess Tarotrei" can only target monsters you control. This skill cannot leave your inventory.

name: Greedging
description: You can only activate "Pot of Greed" if you control "Spirit of the Pot of Greed". "Jar Turtle" is now a Flip Monster, and gains this effect: 'FLIP: Special Summon 1 "Spirit of the Pot of Greed" from your Deck.'. This Skill cannot leave your inventory.

name: Deus-X Machina
description: Negate the second effect of "Deus-X Krawler". This Skill cannot leave your inventory.

name: Going HAM
description: The Fusion materials for "Master of HAM" are 2 Flip Monsters.

name: Small Caves
description: The effect of “Subterror Cave Clash” to gain ATK/DEF only grants 100 ATK/DEF for each set monster on the field instead of 500. This Skill cannot leave your inventory

name: Cataclysmic Prism
description: You can use the effects of "Cataclysmic" monsters, if your Fairy monster is destroyed by an opponent's card, except a "Cataclysmic" monster, regardless of its attribute.

name: The Infinite Cosmos
description: (Once per turn): If a "Starry Knight, Starry Dragon" you control is returned to the hand, draw 1 card.

name: The Great Void
description: During your turn, monsters your opponent controls are also treated as DARK monsters.

name: Frightful Fluffals
description: (Once per Duel): You can discard 1 card; send 1 "Fluffal" card from your Deck to your GY, and if you do, you can add 1 "Toy Vendor" from your GY to your hand.

name: Herald of Fairness
description: Negate the first and second effect of “Herald of the Arc Light”. This Skill cannot leave your inventory.

name: Not the Zero'th Darklord
description: Negate the first effect of "The First Darklord". This Skill cannot leave your inventory.
